ji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T19:14:01.000Z","msg":"電子式好撚抵用<br />\n又唔使擔驚受怕<br />\n拎出放入又放便<br />\n<br />\n基本上一機三鏡或以上就買啦<br />\n或者個箱價佔器材5%或以下都值得買"},{"pid":"a30591aaf4753ee6cebd7e46a085d85c44516753","tid":1959562,"uid":43668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"一勞永逸係無錯"},{"pid":"a1565cf7b1d9c82929549612b620f1a5efabb6c8","tid":1959562,"uid":277302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"絕對要!<br />\n當初貪平買個普通防潮箱, 諗住定期入防潮珠就冇事. 有次大霧帶埋相機行完山, 放返入去箱冇理佢. 最後支鏡起哂菌, 又要花幾百蚊去整. <br />\n之後就立即買個電子防潮箱, 用到而家都無問題"},{"pid":"9214db8f9cbe073fbd7a6743e66955495227e934","tid":1959562,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"要...我有1排冇影相. 個防潮箱俾老母拎咗嚟放海味.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢據為己有. 我要買過第2個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817dad2ba11176a37cc77dda810ead9c71e6cd44","tid":1959562,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"我電子箱，但用防潮珠"},{"pid":"49abdcf13d2eedfa21d2e90de7e2a717a9c7ecff","tid":1959562,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"37f9c04d3ee6db518adef722fc8423b1a096f125","tid":1959562,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"464ccf60608ba00f93d3c52756c2675f24ac0b0a","tid":1959562,"uid":36116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊，買個電子式唔貴得膠箱幾多。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:26:34.000Z","msg":"紅A密氣膠箱都要過三舊，仲未計濕度計同抽濕珠。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\n淘寶淘個電子先2百幾"},{"pid":"b0f4a9fc12910d42483b5ca6226cc20c812b7133","tid":1959562,"uid":248786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"電子for sure<br />\n有聽過話防潮珠唔似電子，會越吸越乾，太乾對鏡頭都唔係一件好事<br />\nAround 45-55%先最好"},{"pid":"d1e2522c9a83ae378a45a0b5b05338abb6fd5